text: <../images/lbar.gif>xiiðusend þæt is legio <ðis> wæs diowla legio.
Ofer ðrim hundradum tribunus bið forwost.
Ine ceorl hæfis wifes gemana ne wif hæfis ceorles on erist<../images/lbar.gif>æfter erest.
Secundum lucanæfter lucan ðus mercong ælces <godspelles> ðe on <tuoelm> byres on lucases dæl.
